<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Properties">Properties</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Square_number&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Properties"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The number <i>m</i> is a square number if and only if one can arrange <i>m</i> points in a square:
</p>
<table cellpadding="8">

<tbody><tr>
