</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/fb4741ee30d4ec6de965a6fd1576bb84c725bb36" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -3.005ex; width:17.735ex; height:6.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle n^{2}=\sum _{k=1}^{n}(2k-1).}"></span>For example, <span class="texhtml">5<sup>2</sup> = 25 = 1 + 3 + 5 + 7 + 9</span>.
</p>
